our relationship completely changed.

02:47.459 --> 02:49.875
The way that we saw each other,

02:50.459 --> 02:52.625
and how’s it’s gonna go into the future.

02:53.167 --> 02:55.583
- We scored an 81 on the Machine.
- Yeah.

02:55.666 --> 02:59.833
And just to have that definite answer
of, no, it’s gonna work, it’s gonna…

03:07.167 --> 03:10.334
At the Relationist Lab,
head designer Cole Ainsley

03:10.417 --> 03:13.833
has been doing groundbreaking work
in the world of AI technology

03:13.917 --> 03:15.583
for almost 15 years.

03:15.666 --> 03:20.791
One of the most important things
in our experience as humans is connection.

03:20.875 --> 03:22.459
We are always looking for connection.

03:22.541 --> 03:25.375
When the board of directors
identified synthetic companions

03:25.459 --> 03:27.209
as the next big growth area,

03:27.292 --> 03:30.500
they hired Ainsley
to run the new offshoot of the company.

03:30.583 --> 03:33.143
I have nothing to do with
the pharmaceutical side of the business.

03:33.167 --> 03:35.791
I’m purely focused on the synthetic lab.

03:35.875 --> 03:40.000
So this then, for example,
is like research for you?

03:40.083 --> 03:42.125
I mean,
this is great if you want a hedge cut.

03:42.209 --> 03:45.459
But I’m much more interested,
not so much in cleaning off the bench,

03:45.541 --> 03:48.125
but who am I gonna be
sitting on that bench with.

03:48.209 --> 03:53.000
And my drive is to create synthetic people
who will become companions for us.

03:53.625 --> 03:57.583
Ultimately, you know, the idea
that you’re safe, that it’s gonna last,

03:57.666 --> 04:00.209
that they’re not... they’re not going to...

04:02.125 --> 04:06.334
They’re not going to leave you is
important, would be important to me, so…

04:07.000 --> 04:10.833
Improving lives through
better relationships is the lab’s mission.

04:17.375 --> 04:18.375
He’s ready for more.

04:18.459 --> 04:19.459
Yeah, he is.

04:19.541 --> 04:23.083
We’re the fastest-growing start-up
in the human relationship market.

04:23.666 --> 04:25.500
We’ve got three divisions:

04:25.583 --> 04:27.708
the Machine, Pharmaceuticals,

04:27.791 --> 04:31.000
and our newest venture,
Synthetic Companions.

04:31.583 --> 04:35.042
I supervise the entire lab
and run the Machine division.

04:35.125 --> 04:37.625
At the Machine,
we evaluate singles, or couples.

04:37.708 --> 04:40.292
