isn’t inside our computers.

05:02.708 --> 05:05.125
It’s inside you.

07:29.167 --> 07:30.875
Just answer honestly.

07:31.708 --> 07:33.209
That’s all you have to do.

07:35.625 --> 07:36.684
We scored an 81…

07:36.708 --> 07:38.125
- Good night.
- Good night.

07:38.209 --> 07:40.583
And just to have that definite answer of,

07:40.666 --> 07:43.750
no, it’s gonna work,
it’s gonna be something that’s for real.

07:54.875 --> 07:55.875
Hi.

07:55.958 --> 07:57.250
Oh, hey.

07:57.334 --> 07:58.791
