09:03.541 --> 09:05.500
Will it be different going forward?

09:07.791 --> 09:09.042
Will...

09:10.583 --> 09:12.083
Will she cheat again?

09:18.583 --> 09:20.167
Is there any way I can make it higher?

09:20.250 --> 09:22.250
There must be a way
I can I make the number…

09:27.791 --> 09:30.000
There has to be a reason
for me to have hope.

09:32.292 --> 09:33.791
Will I hate her?

09:36.791 --> 09:37.875
Do I hate her?

09:40.750 --> 09:42.167
Will I ever get beyond this?

09:47.791 --> 09:49.125
Who is he talking to?

09:50.625 --> 09:53.583
It was a conversation
that I had with the Machine.

09:54.708 --> 09:59.791
Emma and I, we scored very low.
