10:15.750 --> 10:18.666
I’m sorry. I didn’t realize.

10:18.750 --> 10:21.083
Oh, it’s all right. It’s just numbers.

10:21.167 --> 10:24.167
Patterns of activation.
It looks a lot like real emotions.

10:25.666 --> 10:27.417
He’s amazing, really.

10:27.500 --> 10:31.833
No one will feel alone anymore
or feel that kind of pain.

10:32.833 --> 10:35.042
So…

10:36.833 --> 10:38.334
Oh.

10:38.417 --> 10:40.042
It’s Emma. I’ve gotta go.

10:41.750 --> 10:42.750
Cole?

10:44.292 --> 10:45.625
- Yeah.
- Oh.

10:45.708 --> 10:47.334
I-I’ll see you tomorrow, okay?

10:47.958 --> 10:49.209
- Okay.
- Okay.

10:50.042 --> 10:51.042
Okay.

