11:45.167 --> 11:46.750
Where did you find this?

11:46.833 --> 11:49.167
Oh. That was in the basement.

11:49.250 --> 11:52.083
I was gonna maybe, I don’t know,
use her for something.

11:52.167 --> 11:54.726
- Installation or something. Is that okay?
- Yeah, of course, yeah.

11:54.750 --> 11:57.000
