to sleep on their own.

11:59.042 --> 12:01.268
- That’s one good thing, right?
- That came out of the divorce?

12:01.292 --> 12:03.666
- Yeah.
- She’s still got body warmth. Amazing.

12:03.750 --> 12:07.750
Such limited functionality though.
Just a few breathing patterns, that’s all.

12:07.833 --> 12:10.334
- So naive on my part.
- Mmm.

12:10.417 --> 12:13.042
I think it stopped some people
being lonely at night.

12:13.125 --> 12:16.167
