is probably quite spooky.

12:21.334 --> 12:23.334
Hey, thank you for coming tonight.

12:23.417 --> 12:27.209
- It’s really nice of you.
- Yeah, I wouldn’t have missed it.

12:27.791 --> 12:29.851
I liked it. I thought it was good.
Really, really good.

12:29.875 --> 12:31.767
- Thank you.
- Yeah. I thought it was a good show.

12:31.791 --> 12:32.791
Thank you.

12:34.833 --> 12:36.500
Look, I could, uh…

12:37.958 --> 12:42.375
I could leave or… I could stay.

12:42.459 --> 12:46.459
Uh, I started seeing someone.

12:48.750 --> 12:53.708
I mean, I’m trying, you know, to…
I’m just trying to…

12:53.791 --> 12:54.833
Yeah.

12:54.917 --> 12:57.000
I’ve got a really early start tomorrow.

12:57.083 --> 13:00.875
Why don’t you take some time off work,
you know?

13:00.958 --> 13:04.417
I just...
I want you to have the time for yourself.

13:04.541 --> 13:06.250
Maybe find someone.

13:06.334 --> 13:09.083
We’ve got so much work though.
We’ve got the tech summit coming up.

13:09.167 --> 13:11.809
The board of directors wants all heads
of department to show their work.

13:11.833 --> 13:14.833
I get it. I know. I know.
But it’s always…

13:15.541 --> 13:16.791
You always have work.

13:16.875 --> 13:18.417
But I’m fine. I’m good.

13:18.500 --> 13:19.666
- Are you?
- Yes.

13:20.791 --> 13:22.726
- Em, I’m really good.
