14:29.750 --> 14:33.500
Ah. Well… at least we have
something in common.

14:38.209 --> 14:40.125
- When did you come online?
- This morning.

14:40.209 --> 14:43.167
I’ve been doing some research,
some reading.

14:59.625 --> 15:01.125
Your skin, it’s, uh…

15:04.875 --> 15:06.292
softer than mine.

15:09.833 --> 15:11.042
Sorry.

15:13.666 --> 15:16.083
Cole wants to start
my socialization immediately.

15:17.167 --> 15:18.708
