with what you’ve been reading.

15:26.375 --> 15:28.125
Okay. Let’s do that.

15:39.541 --> 15:43.125
Your chances for a successful
relationship are 75 percent.

15:46.083 --> 15:47.459
Congratulations.

15:49.917 --> 15:51.877
I think we can’t help as human beings

15:51.917 --> 15:53.875
