16:57.583 --> 16:59.625
- Okay.
- Yeah?

17:00.209 --> 17:01.917
Sure, we can set that up, yeah.

17:02.791 --> 17:04.459
- Okay.
- Okay.

17:05.583 --> 17:07.083
Go ask her to dance.

17:08.291 --> 17:10.958
Uh, Zoe, would you care to dance?

17:12.209 --> 17:15.000
Yeah.

17:20.041 --> 17:21.875
Okay, looking,
looking at the beautiful lady.

17:21.958 --> 17:23.083
- Yes. Yeah.
- Nice.

17:23.166 --> 17:24.459
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

17:24.540 --> 17:26.334
- Okay.
- It’s nice.

17:27.833 --> 17:30.500
What do you want
your partner to see in you?

17:38.209 --> 17:39.334
I would…

17:41.250 --> 17:44.292
I would like him to see things
no one else does.

17:45.042 --> 17:49.125
What is something you wouldn’t want
your partner to know about you?

17:57.250 --> 17:59.292
I used to be heavy.

18:00.250 --> 18:01.250
Really heavy.

18:03.708 --> 18:06.042
The kind of heavy
that makes you invisible.

18:08.417 --> 18:09.459
And…

18:10.459 --> 18:12.791
I guess I still have trouble with food.

18:16.000 --> 18:19.375
But I would like it
if he didn’t know that.

18:29.708 --> 18:31.459
- You okay, Zoe?
- Yeah.

18:32.292 --> 18:34.167
