for a new drug.

20:53.209 --> 20:54.209
Benzomorphodone.

20:54.625 --> 20:55.917
It’ll be marketed as Benysol.

20:56.833 --> 20:58.875
- What does it cure?
- It doesn’t cure anything.

20:58.958 --> 21:00.541
When you take it with someone else,

21:00.625 --> 21:03.875
it triggers the exact sequence
of hormones and neurotransmitters

21:03.958 --> 21:05.917
that fire when you fall in love.

21:06.000 --> 21:09.417
Not euphoria or mood shifters
like what’s out there now.

21:09.500 --> 21:12.083
This is brand-new and entirely different.

21:12.708 --> 21:15.417
