23:51.042 --> 23:53.500
They’ll take you places you’ve never been.

23:53.583 --> 23:55.541
Does she know what you’re doing to her?

23:55.625 --> 23:56.625
That one?

23:57.334 --> 23:58.708
She’s about to be deactivated.

23:59.750 --> 24:02.500
It isn’t worried, or afraid,
or anything else.

24:03.209 --> 24:06.958
But you can still be with it
in the moments before it’s destroyed,

24:07.042 --> 24:08.833
if that’s your thing.

24:09.666 --> 24:11.042
Because there is no “her.”

24:14.500 --> 24:16.000
Uh-huh.

24:19.833 --> 24:21.125
Cole.

24:21.209 --> 24:22.500
