24:23.209 --> 24:25.833
Wait. I’m so sorry.

24:26.833 --> 24:28.708
That’s not why I brought you down here.

24:28.791 --> 24:30.417
I know. I know.

24:31.917 --> 24:33.125
You know, the other day…

24:34.292 --> 24:36.917
