54:02.167 --> 54:04.000
Not part of a test?

54:04.750 --> 54:06.083
There’s no test.

54:08.541 --> 54:13.000
I could tell, when I told you how I felt,
that you were afraid.

54:13.583 --> 54:15.083
You still are.

54:17.000 --> 54:18.500
But less now.

54:21.625 --> 54:23.875
- You can see that?
- Mm-hmm.

54:54.459 --> 54:58.250
I have memories,
but I’m not sure I know what to do.

54:59.750 --> 55:00.750
Don’t worry.

55:02.042 --> 55:03.750
Just be.

55:03.833 --> 55:05.209
Don’t think.

55:39.083 --> 55:40.334
Good morning.

