56:11.042 --> 56:14.167
You know, there’s different kinds
of relationships, Ash.

56:15.334 --> 56:16.917
Different kinds of love.

56:17.541 --> 56:18.958
Friends can love each other.

56:20.625 --> 56:21.666
Yeah.

56:28.417 --> 56:29.791
What was it like?

56:31.125 --> 56:32.500
To feel so human?

56:42.209 --> 56:43.917
What are you thinking?

56:44.000 --> 56:46.791
It’s a very romantic situation.

56:55.292 --> 56:57.167
I was thinking we should go to Iceland.

56:57.250 --> 56:59.875
And we should get a car
with a tent on the roof,

56:59.958 --> 57:02.459
and we should drive
around the whole island of Iceland

57:02.541 --> 57:05.167
and explore and look at the snow
and the ice floes

57:05.250 --> 57:06.666
and look at shit like that.

57:06.750 --> 57:08.583
New York City.

57:09.958 --> 57:12.917
Where the city never sleeps.

57:13.000 --> 57:15.750
- Why?
- Because we don’t need to sleep there.

57:15.833 --> 57:17.042
But why?

57:19.209 --> 57:20.583
I’m happy here.

57:25.791 --> 57:27.292
Me too.

57:31.666 --> 57:33.334
Can you help me?

57:37.583 --> 57:38.583
Please.

57:39.167 --> 57:41.167
Excuse me, miss. Can you help me?

57:42.583 --> 57:43.708
I’ll be back.

57:44.541 --> 57:46.541
Jesus. I don’t know.

57:54.459 --> 57:55.979
- Zoe! Zoe!
